items.badge_description: After a long day, what better way to kick back than with a crisp and refreshing lager? You're already feeling more relaxed, aren't you?. That's 100 different Lagers! Try 5 more to unlock Level 21.
The battle for grid iron supremacy is on. Who will be the victor? Who are we kidding, with your favorite brew and this badge, you've already won!

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 5 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 2!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 165 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 34.

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 50 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 11!

user.bio: Love craft beers, Imperial Stouts, Double IPA's, Fruit beers, Rauch beers and anything unusual or extreme
